== '''Bhurgeponn''' ==
Bhagevont Paulu  [[Ejipt]] desachea Thebes gan'vchea mullacho zavun aslo. To pondra vorsan'cho aslo tedna tachim`avoi-bapui bhair podllin.To girest aslo ani tannem`voddlem` xikop kel`lem.kristanvank jivexim`martale ani piddapidd ditale tem` polleun to biyelo, ani aplim`Kristi jivit chalu dovrun`k to eka kheddea ghan`vant ghelo.Punn tache bailechea bhavacho ek murti-pujari aslo tannem`tacher arop ghatlo dekhun to Deciusachea hatantlean moron vattavpak Nirjan vattarant pollun ghelo.Dev,apleo soglleo gorzo polleun,apleak teo favo kortolo mhunn Devacher visvas dovorlo ani tachea visvasak lagun Devan taka inam dilo.Je svater to aple tozvizen pavlo hea zagear taka khaupak maddachea foll mellem`.Punn jedna tea maddachim sogllim `follam` kobar zalin tedna suknnim` taka dispott'tim jevonn haddttalin.


Jedna Deciusan kristanvank dhumallo diuncho bhond kelo tedna taka portun aplea ganvghora ien xem `distalem`; punn magnneachi ani tyaganchi taka khup ruch lagli ani tannem` aplim` fuddlem` 90 vorsam` magnneani ani teagani teach zagear salin.

Devak sodtolea Bhag. Antonik fokt tin disan Devan aplem` asnnem` dakhoun dilem.Eka tannel` lea lanngdeak apli tan bhagoun  kudkaxim danvta tem polleun Bhag. Anton tachea fattlean apli tan baghoun kudkaxim ghelo thoim taka Bhag. paulu mell`lo.Jedna Bhag. Anton tache sorxim` aslo tenna suknnim` tankam` dogainkui unddo gheun ietalim`.Akhi rat magnnean sarlea uprant sokallchea fantea parar Bhag.Paulun,Bhag. Antonik apunn mornachea dodder asa oxem sanglem ani taka Bhag. Athanasiusan dill`le mangle ghalun apleak matiek lai mhonn sanglem.Taktin Bhag. Anton tem` anglem` haddunk vetalo tednam` Bhag. Paulucho otmo mhoimen sorgar choddta to deklo.Taka tachi mell`li kudd dimbi ghalun magnnem` korpachea besar mell`li. Dogam` xinvani tacho fond kadlo.

Bhag. Paulu 113 vorsan`chea pirayer sonvsarak ontorlo.Taka vinnpeancho patron oxem` mhonntat.
 
